{
  "stem": "22447.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you couldn't believe what you were-- what you were seeing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You couldn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You didn't know where to look first.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there's people lying in these bunks, in these huts, lying on the floor, lying of top of dead bodies, bodies lying all over the show.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were all looking at you as if to say, you know, you're-- they couldn't believe what we were doing there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't, didn't know what was going on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What, the people, they were--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They didn't have their faculties with them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were a few, a few girls at where we had the information desk.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we had a, a girl come in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She used to spray you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If you wanted to go into the concentration camps, she used to spray them with this DDT, like you shouldn't get with lice.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she, she was reasonably dressed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she had nail varnish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she didn't have her hair shaved.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she looked-- she didn't look too bad.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I said to her, I said that, how is it that you don't look so bad?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You look reasonable.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You got your hair.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You got cosmetics.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, where did you get it from?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She says, look, I'm 21 years old.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I've lost all my family.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I've got no one.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She said, the only way you can stay alive-- if you were fortunate, and you lived with an SS officer, you had something to eat.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Otherwise, you, you, you'd finish up in the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So she said, well, what should I do?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She said, that's the only way you could have stayed alive.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the funny thing is-- the, the Germans have got these funny ways.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was plenty of German Frauleins about.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they had to have Jewish girls for mistresses.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
